aim_western_range by hermione
(new version of "aim_shooting_range")

AIM training map for cs:s
Shoot the orange targets.
Every 10 second, ammo is automatically supplied.

-- new addition --
multiplayer support (8 spawns)
individually score support
buyzone support
3min. game

update 2006/5/17
Allow pickup weapons hanging on the wall. Of course you can buy it also.
2 more targets added.
The gate is auto-open after 15sec.
timeleft display added.
